A4.text: Sue Lyon (in her film debut) as Dolores 'Lolita' Haze

A5.text: The film is deliberately vague over Lolita's age. Kubrick commented, 'I think that some people had the mental picture of a nine-year-old, but Lolita was twelve and a half in the book; Sue Lyon was thirteen.'
